parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the high pressure fuel pump can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power
often while driving at high speeds
the glow plug light flashes
the check engine light comes on
and the vehicle may experience a sudden loss of acceleration.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A fuel system malfunction can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power
often while driving at high speeds
the glow plug light flashes
the check engine light comes on
and the vehicle may experience a sudden loss of acceleration.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A loss of power and stalling can cause the vehicle to lose control, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle loses power
stalls
or experiences a sudden loss of acceleration
often while driving at high speeds.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to serious injury or death in the event of an accident, as the airbags may not deploy properly or at all.
symptoms: The airbag warning indicator illuminates
the airbag system malfunctions
the airbag fails to deploy in an accident
the seat occupancy sensor malfunctions
the airbag system is inoperative despite the passenger being of adequate weight.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay in replacing the Takata airbag can lead to serious injury or death in the event of an accident, as the airbag may rupture or malfunction.
symptoms: The airbag recall notification is received
but the replacement parts are not available
the dealer does not have the necessary parts
the manufacturer fails to provide a remedy or schedule for replacement.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay or failure of the vehicle buyback program can lead to frustration and financial loss for the vehicle owner, as well as potential safety risks due to the vehicle's defects.
symptoms: The vehicle buyback program is delayed or denied
the manufacturer requests repeated documentation
the vehicle is deemed invalid for the program
the owner is left without a resolution or compensation.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden loss of engine power can lead to accidents, especially when driving on highways or in heavy traffic, and can cause the vehicle to stall in dangerous locations, leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine stalls or loses power
the vehicle slows down or comes to a stop
the accelerator pedal becomes unresponsive
the tachometer drops to zero
the vehicle experiences a "hammering effect" or rough idling
white smoke appears at the tailpipe
and the check engine light and glow plug warning light may come on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The defective inter-cooler design can cause the engine to hydro-lock and fail, leading to catastrophic damage and potentially stranding the driver in an unsafe location.
symptoms: Condensation and sludge build up in the charge air intake system
causing the engine to hydro-lock and fail
and potentially resulting in permanent damage.
